                        "AcquisitionStrategy": {
                            "val": "The majority of efforts funded in this project employ a streamlined acquisition approach. Whenever practical, Government-Off-The-Shelf\/Commercial-Off-The-Shelf (GOTS\/COTS) items are tested and evaluated as candidates for solutions to user needs. This normally involves characterization, verification, and qualification testing to ensure GOTS\/COTS equipment is properly certified and adapted for military purposes. However, acquisition strategies may be carried out at the project level for traditional Engineering and Manufacturing Development (EMD), e.g., Integrated Aircrew Ensemble (IAE) and Aircrew Laser Eye Protection (ALEP) Block III."
                        },
